{
    "enabled": true,
    "name": "Test MCP Servers",
    "description": "Test all configured MCP servers and their tools following MCP best practices",
    "version": "2.0",
    "when": {
        "type": "manual",
        "button_text": "Test MCP Servers"
    },
    "then": {
        "type": "askAgent",
        "agentName": "project-test-runner",
        "prompt": "Test MCP server functionality:\n\n**Tests**:\n1. **Connection**: Server startup and handshake\n2. **Tools**: All exposed tools respond correctly\n3. **Resources**: Resource discovery and access\n4. **Error handling**: Graceful failure modes\n\n**Commands**: `mcp test-server`, connection validation\n\n**Output**: MCP server health report with tool availability status",
    }
}